caption: Delicious, highly recommend and definitely coming back

The food is delicious and the service is great too. My friend ordered the Fried Chicken Jianbing and I got the Fried Shrimp Jianbing, both were delicious. It was so good and filling we went back to get another one to share with a friend. I recommend this place if you want to try something new, this something new and delicious. They are located in the second floor, there is also lots of parking in the second floor. 😁 Enjoy!!
